    "visualLanguage": ["light mode", "purple-teal gradient identity", "soft shadows (layered translucent)", "8px radius components", "pill badges", "translucent navbar on scroll"],
    "industry":       "Creative",
    "notes":          "Uses a proprietary sans-serif font. The design system is CSS-in-JS with fully hashed variable names, making token names unreadable — values are recoverable but semantics must be inferred. Root font-size is 10px, so all calc(0.1rem*N) values equal N px directly. Primary brand color is vibrant purple (#8b3dff); the brand gradient runs from teal (#00c4cc) to deep purple (#7d2ae8). Shadows are multi-layer composites with dark navy/blue shadows at low opacity — a signature 'soft elevation' look. Buttons and interactive elements use 8px border-radius (not pill). The navbar is transparent on page load and becomes frosted white (#ffffffcc) on scroll."
  },

